                             17:package org.apache.pdfbox.cos;                                                                                                                                                   
                             18:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             19:import java.io.Closeable;                                                                                                                                                        
                             20:import java.io.FilterOutputStream;                                                                                                                                               
                             21:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             22:import java.io.InputStream;                                                                                                                                                      
                             23:import java.io.OutputStream;                                                                                                                                                     
                             24:import java.util.ArrayList;                                                                                                                                                      
                             25:import java.util.List;                                                                                                                                                           
                             26:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             27:import org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger;                                                                                                                                          
                             28:import org.apache.logging.log4j.LogManager;                                                                                                                                      
                             29:import org.apache.pdfbox.filter.DecodeOptions;                                                                                                                                   
                             30:import org.apache.pdfbox.filter.Filter;                                                                                                                                          
                             31:import org.apache.pdfbox.filter.FilterFactory;                                                                                                                                   
                             32:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.IOUtils;                                                                                                                                             
                             33:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccess;                                                                                                                                        
                             34:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessInputStream;                                                                                                                             
                             35:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessOutputStream;                                                                                                                            
                             36:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessRead;                                                                                                                                    
                             37:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessReadBuffer;                                                                                                                              
                             38:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessReadView;                                                                                                                                
                             39:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessStreamCache;                                                                                                                             
                             40:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             41:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             42: * This class represents a stream object in a PDF document.                                                                                                                      
                             43: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             44: * @author Ben Litchfield                                                                                                                                                        
                             45: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             46:public class COSStream extends COSDictionary implements Closeable                                                                                                                
                             47:{                                                                                                                                                                                
                             48:    // backing store, in-memory or on-disk                                                                                                                                       
                             49:    private RandomAccess randomAccess;                                                                                                                                           
                             50:    // used as a temp buffer when creating a new stream                                                                                                                          
                             51:    private RandomAccessStreamCache streamCache;                                                                                                                                 
                             52:    // indicates if the stream cache was created within this COSStream instance                                                                                                  
                             53:    private boolean closeStreamCache = false;                                                                                                                                    
                             54:    // true if there's an open OutputStream                                                                                                                                      
                             55:    private boolean isWriting;                                                                                                                                                   
                             56:    // random access view to be read from                                                                                                                                        
                             57:    private RandomAccessReadView randomAccessReadView;                                                                                                                           
                             58:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             59:    private static final Logger LOG = LogManager.getLogger(COSStream.class);                                                                                                     
                             60:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             62:     * Creates a new stream with an empty dictionary.                                                                                                                            
                             63:     * <p>                                                                                                                                                                       
                             64:     * Try to avoid using this constructor because it creates a new scratch file in memory. Instead,                                                                             
                             65:     * use {@link COSDocument#createCOSStream() document.getDocument().createCOSStream()} which will                                                                             
                             66:     * use the existing scratch file (in memory or in temp file) of the document.                                                                                                
                             67:     * </p>                                                                                                                                                                      
                             68:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             69:    public COSStream()                                                                                                                                                           
                             70:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             71:        this(null);                                                                                                                                                              
                             72:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             73:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             74:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             75:     * Creates a new stream with an empty dictionary. Data is stored in the given scratch file.                                                                                  
                             76:     *                                                                                                                                                                           
                             77:     * @param streamCache Stream cache for writing stream data.                                                                                                                  
                             78:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             79:    public COSStream(RandomAccessStreamCache streamCache)                                                                                                                        
                             80:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             81:        setInt(COSName.LENGTH, 0);                                                                                                                                               
                             82:        this.streamCache = streamCache;                                                                                                                                          
                             83:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             84:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             85:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             86:     * Creates a new stream with an empty dictionary. Data is read from the given random accessview. Written data is                                                             
                             87:     * stored in the given scratch file.                                                                                                                                         
                             88:     *                                                                                                                                                                           
                             89:     * @param streamCache Stream cache for writing stream data.                                                                                                                  
                             90:     * @param randomAccessReadView source for the data to be read                                                                                                                
                             91:     * @throws IOException if the length of the random access view isn't available                                                                                               
                             92:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             93:    public COSStream(RandomAccessStreamCache streamCache, RandomAccessReadView randomAccessReadView)                                                                             
                             94:            throws IOException                                                                                                                                                   
                             95:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             96:        this(streamCache);                                                                                                                                                       
                             97:        this.randomAccessReadView = randomAccessReadView;                                                                                                                        
                             98:        setInt(COSName.LENGTH, (int) randomAccessReadView.length());                                                                                                             
                             99:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             100:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             101:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             102:     * Throws if the random access backing store has been closed. Helpful for catching cases where                                                                              
                             103:     * a user tries to use a COSStream which has outlived its COSDocument.                                                                                                      
                             104:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             105:    private void checkClosed() throws IOException                                                                                                                               
                             106:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             107:        if (randomAccess != null && randomAccess.isClosed())                                                                                                                    
                             108:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             109:            throw new IOException("COSStream has been closed and cannot be read. " +                                                                                            
                             110:                                  "Perhaps its enclosing PDDocument has been closed?");                                                                                         
                             111:            // Tip for debugging: look at the destination file with an editor, you'll see an                                                                                    
                             112:            // incomplete stream at the bottom.                                                                                                                                 
                             113:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             114:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             115:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             116:    private RandomAccessStreamCache getStreamCache() throws IOException                                                                                                         
                             117:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             118:        if (streamCache == null)                                                                                                                                                
                             119:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             120:            streamCache = IOUtils.createMemoryOnlyStreamCache().create();                                                                                                       
                             121:            closeStreamCache = true;                                                                                                                                            
                             122:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             123:        return streamCache;                                                                                                                                                     
                             124:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             125:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             126:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             127:     * Returns a new InputStream which reads the encoded PDF stream data. Experts only!                                                                                         
                             128:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             129:     * @return InputStream containing raw, encoded PDF stream data.                                                                                                             
                             130:     * @throws IOException If the stream could not be read.                                                                                                                     
                             131:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             132:    public InputStream createRawInputStream() throws IOException                                                                                                                
                             133:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             134:        checkClosed();                                                                                                                                                          
                             135:        if (isWriting)                                                                                                                                                          
                             136:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             137:            throw new IllegalStateException("Cannot read while there is an open stream writer");                                                                                
                             138:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             139:        if (randomAccess == null)                                                                                                                                               
                             140:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             141:            if (randomAccessReadView != null)                                                                                                                                   
                             142:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             143:                randomAccessReadView.seek(0);                                                                                                                                   
                             144:                return new RandomAccessInputStream(randomAccessReadView);                                                                                                       
                             145:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             146:            else                                                                                                                                                                
                             147:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             148:                throw new IOException(                                                                                                                                          
                             149:                        "Create InputStream called without data being written before to stream.");                                                                              
                             150:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             151:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             152:        else                                                                                                                                                                    
                             153:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             154:            return new RandomAccessInputStream(randomAccess);                                                                                                                   
                             155:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             156:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             157:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             158:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             159:     * Returns a new InputStream which reads the decoded stream data.                                                                                                           
                             160:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             161:     * @return InputStream containing decoded stream data.                                                                                                                      
                             162:     * @throws IOException If the stream could not be read.                                                                                                                     
                             163:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             164:    public COSInputStream createInputStream() throws IOException                                                                                                                
                             165:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             166:        return createInputStream(DecodeOptions.DEFAULT);                                                                                                                        
                             167:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             168:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             169:    public COSInputStream createInputStream(DecodeOptions options) throws IOException                                                                                           
                             170:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             171:        InputStream input = createRawInputStream();                                                                                                                             
                             172:        return COSInputStream.create(getFilterList(), this, input, options);                                                                                                    
                             173:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             174:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             175:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             176:     * Returns a new RandomAccessRead which reads the decoded stream data.                                                                                                      
                             177:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             178:     * @return RandomAccessRead containing decoded stream data.                                                                                                                 
                             179:     * @throws IOException If the stream could not be read.                                                                                                                     
                             180:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             181:    public RandomAccessRead createView() throws IOException                                                                                                                     
                             182:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             183:        List<Filter> filterList = getFilterList();                                                                                                                              
                             184:        if (filterList.isEmpty())                                                                                                                                               
                             185:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             186:            if (randomAccess == null && randomAccessReadView != null)                                                                                                           
                             187:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             188:                return new RandomAccessReadView(randomAccessReadView, 0,                                                                                                        
                             189:                        randomAccessReadView.length());                                                                                                                         
                             190:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             191:            else                                                                                                                                                                
                             192:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             193:                return new RandomAccessReadBuffer(createRawInputStream());                                                                                                      
                             194:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             195:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             196:        return Filter.decode(createRawInputStream(), filterList, this, DecodeOptions.DEFAULT, null);                                                                            
                             197:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             198:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             199:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             200:     * Returns a new OutputStream for writing stream data, using the current filters.                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/cos/COSStream.java:1-200

                             17:package org.apache.pdfbox.cos;                                                                                                                                                   
                             18:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             19:import java.io.Closeable;                                                                                                                                                        
                             20:import java.io.FilterOutputStream;                                                                                                                                               
                             21:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             22:import java.io.InputStream;                                                                                                                                                      
                             23:import java.io.OutputStream;                                                                                                                                                     
                             24:import java.util.ArrayList;                                                                                                                                                      
                             25:import java.util.List;                                                                                                                                                           
                             26:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             27:import org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger;                                                                                                                                          
                             28:import org.apache.logging.log4j.LogManager;                                                                                                                                      
                             29:import org.apache.pdfbox.filter.DecodeOptions;                                                                                                                                   
                             30:import org.apache.pdfbox.filter.Filter;                                                                                                                                          
                             31:import org.apache.pdfbox.filter.FilterFactory;                                                                                                                                   
                             32:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.IOUtils;                                                                                                                                             
                             33:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccess;                                                                                                                                        
                             34:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessInputStream;                                                                                                                             
                             35:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessOutputStream;                                                                                                                            
                             36:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessRead;                                                                                                                                    
                             37:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessReadBuffer;                                                                                                                              
                             38:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessReadView;                                                                                                                                
                             39:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessStreamCache;                                                                                                                             
                             40:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             41:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             42: * This class represents a stream object in a PDF document.                                                                                                                      
                             43: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             44: * @author Ben Litchfield                                                                                                                                                        
                             45: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             46:public class COSStream extends COSDictionary implements Closeable                                                                                                                
                             47:{                                                                                                                                                                                
                             48:    // backing store, in-memory or on-disk                                                                                                                                       
                             49:    private RandomAccess randomAccess;                                                                                                                                           
                             50:    // used as a temp buffer when creating a new stream                                                                                                                          
                             51:    private RandomAccessStreamCache streamCache;                                                                                                                                 
                             52:    // indicates if the stream cache was created within this COSStream instance                                                                                                  
                             53:    private boolean closeStreamCache = false;                                                                                                                                    
                             54:    // true if there's an open OutputStream                                                                                                                                      
                             55:    private boolean isWriting;                                                                                                                                                   
                             56:    // random access view to be read from                                                                                                                                        
                             57:    private RandomAccessReadView randomAccessReadView;                                                                                                                           
                             58:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             59:    private static final Logger LOG = LogManager.getLogger(COSStream.class);                                                                                                     
                             60:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             62:     * Creates a new stream with an empty dictionary.                                                                                                                            
                             63:     * <p>                                                                                                                                                                       
                             64:     * Try to avoid using this constructor because it creates a new scratch file in memory. Instead,                                                                             
                             65:     * use {@link COSDocument#createCOSStream() document.getDocument().createCOSStream()} which will                                                                             
                             66:     * use the existing scratch file (in memory or in temp file) of the document.                                                                                                
                             67:     * </p>                                                                                                                                                                      
                             68:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             69:    public COSStream()                                                                                                                                                           
                             70:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             71:        this(null);                                                                                                                                                              
                             72:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             73:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             74:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             75:     * Creates a new stream with an empty dictionary. Data is stored in the given scratch file.                                                                                  
                             76:     *                                                                                                                                                                           
                             77:     * @param streamCache Stream cache for writing stream data.                                                                                                                  
                             78:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             79:    public COSStream(RandomAccessStreamCache streamCache)                                                                                                                        
                             80:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             81:        setInt(COSName.LENGTH, 0);                                                                                                                                               
                             82:        this.streamCache = streamCache;                                                                                                                                          
                             83:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             84:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             85:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             86:     * Creates a new stream with an empty dictionary. Data is read from the given random accessview. Written data is                                                             
                             87:     * stored in the given scratch file.                                                                                                                                         
                             88:     *                                                                                                                                                                           
                             89:     * @param streamCache Stream cache for writing stream data.                                                                                                                  
                             90:     * @param randomAccessReadView source for the data to be read                                                                                                                
                             91:     * @throws IOException if the length of the random access view isn't available                                                                                               
                             92:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             93:    public COSStream(RandomAccessStreamCache streamCache, RandomAccessReadView randomAccessReadView)                                                                             
                             94:            throws IOException                                                                                                                                                   
                             95:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             96:        this(streamCache);                                                                                                                                                       
                             97:        this.randomAccessReadView = randomAccessReadView;                                                                                                                        
                             98:        setInt(COSName.LENGTH, (int) randomAccessReadView.length());                                                                                                             
                             99:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             100:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             101:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             102:     * Throws if the random access backing store has been closed. Helpful for catching cases where                                                                              
                             103:     * a user tries to use a COSStream which has outlived its COSDocument.                                                                                                      
                             104:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             105:    private void checkClosed() throws IOException                                                                                                                               
                             106:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             107:        if (randomAccess != null && randomAccess.isClosed())                                                                                                                    
                             108:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             109:            throw new IOException("COSStream has been closed and cannot be read. " +                                                                                            
                             110:                                  "Perhaps its enclosing PDDocument has been closed?");                                                                                         
                             111:            // Tip for debugging: look at the destination file with an editor, you'll see an                                                                                    
                             112:            // incomplete stream at the bottom.                                                                                                                                 
                             113:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             114:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             115:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             116:    private RandomAccessStreamCache getStreamCache() throws IOException                                                                                                         
                             117:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             118:        if (streamCache == null)                                                                                                                                                
                             119:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             120:            streamCache = IOUtils.createMemoryOnlyStreamCache().create();                                                                                                       
                             121:            closeStreamCache = true;                                                                                                                                            
                             122:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             123:        return streamCache;                                                                                                                                                     
                             124:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             125:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             126:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             127:     * Returns a new InputStream which reads the encoded PDF stream data. Experts only!                                                                                         
                             128:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             129:     * @return InputStream containing raw, encoded PDF stream data.                                                                                                             
                             130:     * @throws IOException If the stream could not be read.                                                                                                                     
                             131:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             132:    public InputStream createRawInputStream() throws IOException                                                                                                                
                             133:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             134:        checkClosed();                                                                                                                                                          
                             135:        if (isWriting)                                                                                                                                                          
                             136:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             137:            throw new IllegalStateException("Cannot read while there is an open stream writer");                                                                                
                             138:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             139:        if (randomAccess == null)                                                                                                                                               
                             140:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             141:            if (randomAccessReadView != null)                                                                                                                                   
                             142:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             143:                randomAccessReadView.seek(0);                                                                                                                                   
                             144:                return new RandomAccessInputStream(randomAccessReadView);                                                                                                       
                             145:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             146:            else                                                                                                                                                                
                             147:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             148:                throw new IOException(                                                                                                                                          
                             149:                        "Create InputStream called without data being written before to stream.");                                                                              
                             150:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             151:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             152:        else                                                                                                                                                                    
                             153:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             154:            return new RandomAccessInputStream(randomAccess);                                                                                                                   
                             155:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             156:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             157:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             158:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             159:     * Returns a new InputStream which reads the decoded stream data.                                                                                                           
                             160:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             161:     * @return InputStream containing decoded stream data.                                                                                                                      
                             162:     * @throws IOException If the stream could not be read.                                                                                                                     
                             163:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             164:    public COSInputStream createInputStream() throws IOException                                                                                                                
                             165:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             166:        return createInputStream(DecodeOptions.DEFAULT);                                                                                                                        
                             167:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             168:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             169:    public COSInputStream createInputStream(DecodeOptions options) throws IOException                                                                                           
                             170:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             171:        InputStream input = createRawInputStream();                                                                                                                             
                             172:        return COSInputStream.create(getFilterList(), this, input, options);                                                                                                    
                             173:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             174:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             175:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             176:     * Returns a new RandomAccessRead which reads the decoded stream data.                                                                                                      
                             177:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             178:     * @return RandomAccessRead containing decoded stream data.                                                                                                                 
                             179:     * @throws IOException If the stream could not be read.                                                                                                                     
                             180:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             181:    public RandomAccessRead createView() throws IOException                                                                                                                     
                             182:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             183:        List<Filter> filterList = getFilterList();                                                                                                                              
                             184:        if (filterList.isEmpty())                                                                                                                                               
                             185:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             186:            if (randomAccess == null && randomAccessReadView != null)                                                                                                           
                             187:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             188:                return new RandomAccessReadView(randomAccessReadView, 0,                                                                                                        
                             189:                        randomAccessReadView.length());                                                                                                                         
                             190:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             191:            else                                                                                                                                                                
                             192:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             193:                return new RandomAccessReadBuffer(createRawInputStream());                                                                                                      
                             194:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             195:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             196:        return Filter.decode(createRawInputStream(), filterList, this, DecodeOptions.DEFAULT, null);                                                                            
                             197:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             198:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             199:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             200:     * Returns a new OutputStream for writing stream data, using the current filters.                                                                                           
                             ```
