                             154:    private void readNextValue(byte[] value) throws IOException                                                                                                                 
                             155:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             156:        int remainingBytes = value.length;                                                                                                                                      
                             157:        int amountRead;                                                                                                                                                         
                             158:        while ((amountRead = source.read(value, value.length - remainingBytes, remainingBytes)) > 0)                                                                            
                             159:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             160:            remainingBytes -= amountRead;                                                                                                                                       
                             161:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             162:    }

                             pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFXrefStreamParser.java:182-212                                                                                                   
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             182:        private ObjectNumbers(COSArray indexArray) throws IOException                                                                                                           
                             183:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             184:            start = new long[indexArray.size() / 2];                                                                                                                            
                             185:            end = new long[start.length];                                                                                                                                       
                             186:            int counter = 0;                                                                                                                                                    
                             187:            Iterator<COSBase> indexIter = indexArray.iterator();                                                                                                                
                             188:            while (indexIter.hasNext())                                                                                                                                         
                             189:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             190:                COSBase base = indexIter.next();                                                                                                                                
                             191:                if (!(base instanceof COSInteger))                                                                                                                              
                             192:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             193:                    throw new IOException("Xref stream must have integer in /Index array");                                                                                     
                             194:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             195:                long startValue = ((COSInteger) base).longValue();                                                                                                              
                             196:                if (!indexIter.hasNext())                                                                                                                                       
                             197:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             198:                    break;                                                                                                                                                      
                             199:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             200:                base = indexIter.next();                                                                                                                                        
                             201:                if (!(base instanceof COSInteger))                                                                                                                              
                             202:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             203:                    throw new IOException("Xref stream must have integer in /Index array");                                                                                     
                             204:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             205:                long sizeValue = ((COSInteger) base).longValue();                                                                                                               
                             206:                start[counter] = startValue;                                                                                                                                    
                             207:                end[counter] = startValue + sizeValue;                                                                                                                          
                             208:                counter++;                                                                                                                                                      
                             209:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             210:            currentNumber = start[0];                                                                                                                                           
                             211:            currentEnd = end[0];                                                                                                                                                
                             212:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>

                             188:        // remember the highest XRef object number to avoid it being reused in incremental saving                                                                               
                             189:        Optional<Long> maxValue = document.getXrefTable().keySet().stream() //                                                                                                  
                             190:                .map(COSObjectKey::getNumber) //                                                                                                                                
                             191:                .reduce(Long::max);                                                                                                                                             
                             192:        document.setHighestXRefObjectNumber(maxValue.isPresent() ? maxValue.get() : 0);                                                                                         
                             193:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             194:        return trailer;                                                                                                                                                         
                             195:    }

                             ===Issue===                                                                                                                                                                         
                             ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             ===Evaluation Report===                                                                                                                                                             
                             # Evaluation Report                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             ## Summary                                                                                                                                                                          
                             The initial issue is a libFuzzer timeout during PDFBox fuzzing (no crash or exception beyond timeout). A patch was applied to PDFXrefStreamParser.java: it adds                   
                             reasonable-bounds checks on the sum of the `/W` array fields (`MAX_W_SUM`) and caps the total number of XRef entries processed (`MAX_XREF_ENTRIES`). After applying                 
                             the patch, the fuzzer still times out at the same point, with the main thread stuck in `org.apache.fontbox.type1.Type1Parser.readEncoding`.                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             ## Description                                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             1. Initial Issue                                                                                                                                                                    
                                - Fuzzer invocation reports only `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout` after ~27 seconds.                                                                                                  
                                - No crash, exception, or stack overflowjust a hang.                                                                                                                            
                                - Thread dump shows the main thread executing inside `com.code_intelligence.jazzer.runtime.TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceConstCmpInt`, called from                           
                             `org.apache.fontbox.type1.Type1Parser.readEncoding`. The fuzz target is `PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`.                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             2. Patch Attempt                                                                                                                                                                    
                                - File modified:                                                                                                                                                                 
                                  `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFXrefStreamParser.java`                                                                                                    
                                - Additions:                                                                                                                                                                     
                                   `private static final long MAX_XREF_ENTRIES = 1_000_000L;`                                                                                                                   
                                   `private static final int    MAX_W_SUM         = 1024;`                                                                                                                      
                                - In the constructor or earlier validation:                                                                                                                                      
                                   Compute `long wSum = (long) w[0] + w[1] + w[2];`                                                                                                                             
                                   If `wSum == 0 || wSum > MAX_W_SUM`  throw `IOException`.                                                                                                                    
                                - In `parse(XrefTrailerResolver resolver)`:                                                                                                                                      
                                   Introduce `long processedEntries = 0;`                                                                                                                                       
                                   On each loop iteration increment it; if it exceeds `MAX_XREF_ENTRIES`, throw `IOException`.                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             3. Patch Result                                                                                                                                                                     
                                - After rebuilding with these checks, the fuzzer run still ends in a timeout.                                                                                                    
                                - The full thread dump remains largely unchanged: the main thread is still busy in `Type1Parser.readEncoding`.                                                                   
                                - No new exception is thrown from PDFXrefStreamParser; the hang has moved beyond XRef parsing into font parsing.                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             4. Key Observations & Further Investigation Areas                                                                                                                                   
                                - The timeout is not in PDFXrefStreamParser; the fuzzer quickly reaches font parsing (`Type1Parser.readEncoding`) and stalls there.                                              
                                - The harness (`PDFExtractTextFuzzer`) drives parsing through PDFTextStripper, invoking `Type1Font.createWithPFB`.                                                               
                                - The hang path involves:                                                                                                                                                        
                                  PDFStreamEngine  PDFTextStripper  PDType1Font  Type1Parser.parseASCII/readEncoding.                                                                                         
                                - Investigate the Type1 font parser in fontbox: loops over encoding/data sections may lack bounds checks or exit conditions.                                                     
                                - Review ASCII vs. binary PFB segment handling, looking for infinite loops or unbounded reads in `Type1Parser`.                                                                  
                                - Examine interaction between Jazzers data-flow callbacks and the native read routines (`TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceConstCmpInt`).                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             No speculation on root causes or solutions is provided. The focus should be on the font parsing modules (org.apache.fontbox.type1) and how they process PFB data                    
                             under fuzzed inputs.                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             ## Initial Issue Log                                                                                                                                                                
                             Here is the initial issue log of the codebase:                                                                                                                                      
                             <issue>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </issue>

                             12: * distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS,                                                                                                             
                             13: * WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.                                                                                                      
                             14: * See the License for the specific language governing permissions and                                                                                                           
                             15: * limitations under the License.                                                                                                                                                
                             16: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             17:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             18:package org.apache.fontbox.type1;                                                                                                                                                
                             19:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             20:import org.apache.fontbox.encoding.BuiltInEncoding;                                                                                                                              
                             21:import org.apache.fontbox.encoding.StandardEncoding;                                                                                                                             
                             22:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             23:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             24:import java.util.ArrayList;                                                                                                                                                      
                             25:import java.util.HashMap;                                                                                                                                                        
                             26:import java.util.List;                                                                                                                                                           
                             27:import java.util.Map;                                                                                                                                                            
                             28:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             29:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             30: * Parses an Adobe Type 1 (.pfb) font. It is used exclusively by Type1Font.                                                                                                      
                             31: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             32: * The Type 1 font format is a free-text format which is somewhat difficult                                                                                                      
                             33: * to parse. This is made worse by the fact that many Type 1 font files do                                                                                                       
                             34: * not conform to the specification, especially those embedded in PDFs. This                                                                                                     
                             35: * parser therefore tries to be as forgiving as possible.                                                                                                                        
                             36: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             37: * @see "Adobe Type 1 Font Format, Adobe Systems (1999)"                                                                                                                         
                             38: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             39: * @author John Hewson                                                                                                                                                           
                             40: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             41:final class Type1Parser                                                                                                                                                          
                             42:{                                                                                                                                                                                
                             43:    // constants for encryption                                                                                                                                                  
                             44:    private static final int EEXEC_KEY = 55665;                                                                                                                                  
                             45:    private static final int CHARSTRING_KEY = 4330;                                                                                                                              
                             46:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             47:    // state                                                                                                                                                                     
                             48:    private Type1Lexer lexer;                                                                                                                                                    
                             49:    private Type1Font font;                                                                                                                                                      
                             50:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             51:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             52:     * Parses a Type 1 font and returns a Type1Font class which represents it.                                                                                                   
                             53:     *                                                                                                                                                                           
                             54:     * @param segment1 Segment 1: ASCII                                                                                                                                          
                             55:     * @param segment2 Segment 2: Binary                                                                                                                                         
                             56:     * @throws IOException                                                                                                                                                       
                             57:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             58:    public Type1Font parse(byte[] segment1, byte[] segment2) throws IOException                                                                                                  
                             59:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             60:        font = new Type1Font(segment1, segment2);                                                                                                                                
                             61:        try                                                                                                                                                                      
                             62:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             63:            parseASCII(segment1);                                                                                                                                                
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java:192-239                                                                                                             
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             192:    private void readEncoding() throws IOException                                                                                                                              
                             193:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             194:        if (lexer.peekKind(Token.NAME))                                                                                                                                         
                             195:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             196:            String name = lexer.nextToken().getText();                                                                                                                          
                             197:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             198:            if (name.equals("StandardEncoding"))                                                                                                                                
                             199:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             200:                font.encoding = StandardEncoding.INSTANCE;                                                                                                                      
                             201:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             202:            else                                                                                                                                                                
                             203:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             204:                throw new IOException("Unknown encoding: " + name);                                                                                                             
                             205:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             206:            readMaybe(Token.NAME, "readonly");                                                                                                                                  
                             207:            read(Token.NAME, "def");                                                                                                                                            
                             208:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             209:        else                                                                                                                                                                    
                             210:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             211:            read(Token.INTEGER).intValue();                                                                                                                                     
                             212:            readMaybe(Token.NAME, "array");                                                                                                                                     
                             213:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             214:            // 0 1 255 {1 index exch /.notdef put } for                                                                                                                         
                             215:            // we have to check "readonly" and "def" too                                                                                                                        
                             216:            // as some fonts don't provide any dup-values, see PDFBOX-2134                                                                                                      
                             217:            while (!(lexer.peekKind(Token.NAME)                                                                                                                                 
                             218:                    && (lexer.peekToken().getText().equals("dup")                                                                                                               
                             219:                            || lexer.peekToken().getText().equals("readonly")                                                                                                   
                             220:                            || lexer.peekToken().getText().equals("def"))))                                                                                                     
                             221:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             222:                lexer.nextToken();                                                                                                                                              
                             223:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             224:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             225:            Map<Integer, String> codeToName = new HashMap<>();                                                                                                                  
                             226:            while (lexer.peekKind(Token.NAME) &&                                                                                                                                
                             227:                    lexer.peekToken().getText().equals("dup"))                                                                                                                  
                             228:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             229:                read(Token.NAME, "dup");                                                                                                                                        
                             230:                int code = read(Token.INTEGER).intValue();                                                                                                                      
                             231:                String name = read(Token.LITERAL).getText();                                                                                                                    
                             232:                read(Token.NAME, "put");                                                                                                                                        
                             233:                codeToName.put(code, name);                                                                                                                                     
                             234:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             235:            font.encoding = new BuiltInEncoding(codeToName);                                                                                                                    
                             236:            readMaybe(Token.NAME, "readonly");                                                                                                                                  
                             237:            read(Token.NAME, "def");                                                                                                                                            
                             238:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             239:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>

                             123:            while (buffer.hasRemaining())                                                                                                                                       
                             124:            {

                             126:

                             129:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             130:                    // comment

                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.java:119-162                                                                                                              
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             119:        boolean skip;                                                                                                                                                           
                             120:        do                                                                                                                                                                      
                             121:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             122:            skip = false;                                                                                                                                                       
                             123:            while (buffer.hasRemaining())                                                                                                                                       
                             124:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             125:                char c = getChar();                                                                                                                                             
                             126:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             127:                // delimiters                                                                                                                                                   
                             128:                if (c == '%')                                                                                                                                                   
                             129:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             130:                    // comment                                                                                                                                                  
                             131:                    readComment();                                                                                                                                              
                             132:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             133:                else if (c == '(')                                                                                                                                              
                             134:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             135:                    return readString();                                                                                                                                        
                             136:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             137:                else if (c == ')')                                                                                                                                              
                             138:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             139:                    // not allowed outside a string context                                                                                                                     
                             140:                    throw new IOException("unexpected closing parenthesis");                                                                                                    
                             141:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             142:                else if (c == '[')                                                                                                                                              
                             143:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             144:                    return new Token(c, Token.START_ARRAY);                                                                                                                     
                             145:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             146:                else if (c == '{')                                                                                                                                              
                             147:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             148:                    return new Token(c, Token.START_PROC);                                                                                                                      
                             149:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             150:                else if (c == ']')                                                                                                                                              
                             151:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             152:                    return new Token(c, Token.END_ARRAY);                                                                                                                       
                             153:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             154:                else if (c == '}')                                                                                                                                              
                             155:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             156:                    return new Token(c, Token.END_PROC);                                                                                                                        
                             157:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             158:                else if (c == '/')                                                                                                                                              
                             159:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             160:                    String regular = readRegular();                                                                                                                             
                             161:                    if (regular == null)                                                                                                                                        
                             162:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>

                             190:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             191:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             192:    private void readEncoding() throws IOException                                                                                                                              
                             193:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             194:        if (lexer.peekKind(Token.NAME))                                                                                                                                         
                             195:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             196:            String name = lexer.nextToken().getText();

                             200:                font.encoding = StandardEncoding.INSTANCE;                                                                                                                      
                             201:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             202:            else

                             213:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             214:            // 0 1 255 {1 index exch /.notdef put } for                                                                                                                         
                             215:            // we have to check "readonly" and "def" too

                             228:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             229:                read(Token.NAME, "dup");                                                                                                                                        
                             230:                int code = read(Token.INTEGER).intValue();

                             241:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             242:     * Extracts values from an array as numbers.                                                                                                                                
                             243:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             244:    private List<Number> arrayToNumbers(List<Token> value) throws IOException                                                                                                   
                             245:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             246:        List<Number> numbers = new ArrayList<>();                                                                                                                               
                             247:        for (int i = 1, size = value.size() - 1; i < size; i++)                                                                                                                 
                             248:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             249:            Token token = value.get(i);                                                                                                                                         
                             250:            if (token.getKind() == Token.REAL)                                                                                                                                  
                             ```

                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFXrefStreamParser.java:1-200                                                                                                     
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             1:/*

                             10: *
